				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Counter Warfare: The Surprisingly Strategic Party Royale" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>Do you like Battle Royales and getting together with your friends?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We made a Battle Royale you can get together and play with your friends!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;By combining the simplicity of a party game with the strategy of competitive trading card games, Counter Warfare lets you drop in and have a great time fighting your 'IRL' friends and fam over-and-over-and-over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is made of 104 Unique, Balanced, Beautiful cards, divided into 2 card types and 4 rarities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take turns choosing the best play for their turn to get rid of all opponent cards while still keeping some in their hand.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, your cards are your life, so there are no trackers, dice, or anything else required to play the game. Just the cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game also takes an average of 3 minutes to learn due to the fact that all the cards tell you exactly how to play them, and there are no other resources required.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When the deck runs out, players discard cards on their turn instead of drawing, ensuring that there will always only be 1 winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has a ton of humor in it, and is great for 1v1's and small groups.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are constantly coming up with plans that other players are constantly ruining, and emotions can get playfully heated!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The lighthearted design of the cards adds a great personal touch to the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
